    {
      "id": "intro_2",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The search for oil",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 2.42,
      "endTime": 10.78
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_3",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "What do oilmen want to achieve as soon as they strike oil?",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 10.79,
      "endTime": 16.97,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "intro_4",
      "role": "Narrator",
      "text": "The deepest holes of all are made for oil, and they go down to as much as 25, 000 feet.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 16.98,
      "endTime": 26.08,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Much",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "非常"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s1",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "But we do not need to send man down to get the oil out, as we must with other mineral deposits.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 26.09,
      "endTime": 34.3,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Not",
            "pos": "adv.",
            "meaning": "不，不是"
          },
          {
            "word": "Man",
            "pos": "n.",
            "meaning": "男人"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s2",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "The holes are only borings, less than a foot in diameter.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 34.31,
      "endTime": 40.17,
      "analysis": {
        "words": []
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s3",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "My particular experience is largely in oil, and the search for oil has done more to improve deep drilling than any other mining activity.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 40.18,
      "endTime": 52.3,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "My",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "我的"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s4",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "When it has been decided where we are going to drill,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 52.31,
      "endTime": 56.07,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s5",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "we put up at the surface an oil derrick.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 56.08,
      "endTime": 59.83,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s6",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "It has to be tall because it is like a giant block and tackle and we have to lower into the ground",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 59.84,
      "endTime": 66.81,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Tall",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "高的"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s7",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "and haul out of the ground great lengths of drill pipe which are rotated by an engine at the top",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 66.82,
      "endTime": 73.83,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s8",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "and are fitted with a cutting bit at the bottom.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 73.84,
      "endTime": 77.94,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "At",
            "pos": "prep.",
            "meaning": "在...（小地点/时刻）"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s9",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "The geologist needs to know what rocks the drill has reached,",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 77.95,
      "endTime": 82.66,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "What",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "什么"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s10",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "so every so often a sample is obtained with a coring bit.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 82.67,
      "endTime": 88.1,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s11",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "It cuts a clean cylinder of rock, from which can be seen the strata the drill has been cutting through.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 88.11,
      "endTime": 96.44,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s12",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "Once we get down to the oil, it usually flows to the surface because great pressure either from gas or water, is pushing it.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 96.45,
      "endTime": 106.92,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          },
          {
            "word": "Is",
            "pos": "v.",
            "meaning": "是"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s13",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "This pressure must be under control, and we control it by means of the mud which we circulate down the drill pipe.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 106.93,
      "endTime": 116.21,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "This",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "这，这个"
          },
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s14",
      "role": "Woman",
      "text": "We endeavour to avoid the old, romantic idea of a gusher, which wastes oil and gas.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 116.22,
      "endTime": 124.32,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "Old",
            "pos": "adj.",
            "meaning": "老的，旧的"
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s15",
      "role": "Man",
      "text": "We want it to stay down the hole until we can lead it off in a controlled manner.",
      "translation": "",
      "startTime": 124.33,
      "endTime": 129.33,
      "analysis": {
        "words": [
          {
            "word": "It",
            "pos": "pron.",
            "meaning": "它"
          }
        ]
      }
    }
  ]
